{"tid":1956504,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局正與聯儲局了解操作細節，亦正設計相關機制讓銀行可以取得美元流動性。","createTime":"2020-04-03T08:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T08:56:06.000Z","uid":197121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9670c3e625be8b8e77e1f3f5b2b1f884af72d82","tid":1956504,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518682-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518682-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=9c8e6812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518682-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b4280c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518682-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n金管局表示，為確保銀行間市場及銀行體系運作暢順，已經或將會採取措施管理流動性，亦準備好在現有監管框架下增加靈活性。<br />\n<br />\n有關流動性措施涉及3方面，包括流動資金安排框架方面，金管局考慮為備用流動資金安排(SLF)自動續期，解決銀行長期資金需求，並為有關資金定價，幫助減低市場波動性。<br />\n<br />\n金管局亦鼓勵銀行使用之前建立的資金緩衝，應對流動性需求及支持經濟活動，並容許銀行相關流動性比率暫時處於較低水平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，聯儲局早前宣布，為海外央行及國際金融機構設立臨時回購協議安排，為期6個月。金管局正與聯儲局了解操作細節，亦正設計相關機制讓銀行可以取得美元流動性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銀行唔夠錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3843a300b045b6340ac1c563a7e595b4ab39736","tid":1956504,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9670c3e625be8b8e77e1f3f5b2b1f884af72d82","tid":1956504,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518682-20200403.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518682-20200403.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bt%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=9c8e6812\" data-ef-url=\"http